        @GET
 @Produces(value="application/json")

                                                                                                          String id,

        Retrieves either a remote or local tooltip
        Parameters:
        id - unique identifier for entry whose tooltip is to be retrieved

        fid - required if isRemote is true. The remote entry should be shared in this folder
        Returns:
        PartData information about the entry with enough information to show the tooltip

      • create

        @POST
 @Consumes(value="application/json")
 @Produces(value="application/json")
public javax.ws.rs.core.Response create(@QueryParam(value="source")
                                                                                                                        String sourceId,
                                                                                                                        PartData partData)
        Creates a new entry. If the sourceId parameter is set, the new entry is a copy of the source id (if found) otherwise the new entry is created from the data contained in the partData
        Parameters:
        sourceId - optional unique identifier for an existing part to copy. If not set, the partData parameter must be set
        partData - optional data for creating new entry. if not set, then the sourceId must be set
        Returns:
        wrapper around identifier for newly created part which can be used to retrieve it
